These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-1::.
3 different games are played: snooker, scrabble, go
The people have 3 different hobbies: traveling, skydiving, rock-climbing
1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is in the middle##1
2. the person playing go is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
3. the person playing snooker is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |    3    |
| Game   | snooker | scrabble | go   |
| Hobby      | traveling    | skydiving  | rock-climbing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-2::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daffodil, lily, begonia
3 different games are played: mah-jongg, billiard, snooker
1. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
2. the person playing billiard is on the far left##1
3. the person playing billiard is the person who growslily##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |
| Flower      | lily | daffodil     | begonia      |
| Game   | billiard | mah-jongg | snooker |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-3::.
House: gothic-revival, craftsman, modern
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, baccarat, blend
1. the craftsman house is on the right of the baccarat-smoker##1
2. the modern house is on the left of the blend-smoker##1
3. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |     3     |
| House   | gothic-revival | modern  | craftsman       |
| Cigar       | dannemann     | baccarat | blend |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-4::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  fisherman, bartender, teacher
3 different games are played: backgammon, monopoly, canasta
1. the bartender is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
2. the fisherman is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
3. the person playing canasta is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |      3      |
| Job    | teacher    | bartender     | fisherman |
| Game   | canasta | backgammon | monopoly     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-5::.
House: craftsman, modern, wooden
The people have 3 different hobbies: sudoku, puzzles, chess
1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the wooden house##1
2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the craftsman house##1
3. the wooden house is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
4. the craftsman house is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3     |
| House         | modern | craftsman     | wooden |
| Hobby   | chess        | sudoku | puzzles    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-6::.
City: paris, new-york, colone
There are 3 different favourite colors: light-blue, azure, white
1. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1
2. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the person who likes azure##1
3. the person traveling to colone is the person who likes light-blue##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |   3   |
| City        | colone | paris      | new-york  |
| Color   | light-blue       | azure | white |

 #################################

 
