.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-8::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: trike, airplane, scooter
3 different games are played: monopoly, go, backgammon
1. the person playing go is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
2. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
3. the person driving the airplane is the person playing go##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |
| Transport    | scooter | trike | airplane      |
| Game   | monopoly     | backgammon | go |

