.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-9::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, dannemann, vegafina
There 3 different types of food: banana, watermelon, cabbage
1. the person eating banana is the dannemann-smoker##1
2. the person eating watermelon is on the far right##1
3. the dannemann-smoker is on the right of the vegafina-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Cigar   | vegafina | dannemann | davidoff  |
| Food     | cabbage     | banana      | watermelon |

