2. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person who likes red##1
3. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |
| Color   | fuchsia | turquise   | red  |
| Beverage   | lemonade    | coffee | tea |

