2. the person driving the helicopter is the person playing bridge##1
3. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |
| Transport         | snowmobile | helicopter | boat |
| Game   | canasta | bridge     | mah-jongg  |

