.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-20::.
3 different pets are kept: frog, mouse, rabbit
House: cape-cod, ranch-style, tower
1. the ranch-style house is in the middle##1
2. the tower house is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
3. the owner of the mouse is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2       |    3    |
| Pet    | rabbit | frog       | mouse  |
| House   | tower  | ranch-style | cape-cod |

 